summary: Dan and Phil Interactive Introvert Ticket For Sale
title: Dan and Phil Interactive Introvert Ticket For Sale
body:
So, I was scheduled to work on the day of Dan and Phil’s tour stop in Seattle, which means that I have a ticket to sell to Interactive Introverts at 3pm on August 11th. That’s this Saturday. 

It is in the 2nd section of the audience and it is a general admission ticket, and it has parking at the auditorium that I paid for that comes with the ticket. I paid, counting all the fees and the ticket price, about 60 dollars for the ticket. I’m selling it for 45 dollars. 

I know it’s a little late to sell a ticket, oops… But I figure if I can’t go, I want to see if I can help someone else go! If you are interested, dm me and we can work out details with paypal and ticket name changes and so on. You will have to be comfortable with giving me your name and email address for this to work, and according to ticketmaster’s rules, you must be over 14 to go alone. I only have one ticket, so you’ll have to be alone.

summary: Thank you @amazingphil and @danielhowell for one of the most amazing nights of my life. The show was incredible and represented...
body: Thank you @amazingphil and @danielhowell for one of the most amazing nights of my life. The show was incredible and represented who you guys are perfectly. It was the perfect blend of being serious and comedic skits. I’ve been having a hard time lately and seeing you guys made me 1000% happier. I’m super proud of you guys and hope you keep on being wonderful people 💖💖 (and yes I did dress as phil for the show 😂)
